Release Checklist

-1) Notify gallery-redistributors list of upcoming release

0) Make sure all unit tests pass

1) Update the gallery3 VERSION constant in galler3/modules/gallery/helpers/gallery.php

2) Look over gallery3/README and touch up anything version specific

3) Tag the release, eg:
   $ git tag 3.0-rc-2
   $ git push --tags

4) Build the release, eg:
   php build.php 3.0-rc-2

5) Publish the release to sf.net
   rsync -avP -e ssh dist/gallery-3.0-rc-2.zip bharat@frs.sourceforge.net:uploads/

6) <insert docs about updating SF.net FRS stuff here>

7) Create a forum topic for the release

8) One final pass over the GMC news story, make sure the download link is correct.

9) Click "publish" on the GMC story

10) Update the release date on the Codex

11) Update sf.net, freshmeat.net, opensourcecms.com stories

12) E-mail gallery-announce and gallery-redistributors announcing the releas, linking to the GMC story and download URL

13) Close the old milestone

